Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天不吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 偶爾早點去學校也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把這個扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  變熟練了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很溫柔對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡啊  真的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  我是小津
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小津三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你喜歡什麼味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝麻味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝麻味？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打鈴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作文寫好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放學後也到圖書室來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要進行避難訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得帶防災頭巾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經無處可逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一件事要告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於前幾天佐伯同學的體操服被偷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實那天放學後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本校的學生看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校周圍有可疑的男子在徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是三十歲左右的長髮眼鏡男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果看見可疑人員馬上向老師匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後立刻回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊抓住犯人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  我如果被做了奇怪的事情該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日  變有趣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈子  別太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控著我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我們沉溺於罪惡的美色靡靡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每日一步步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邁入地獄的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無驚悚地穿過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發著惡臭的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快讓我看看作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波爾萊爾的詩集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡之花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最喜歡的詩集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本書中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流淌蔓延著陰暗的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是生活在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一輩子都無法理解的哲學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 臭蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看的是將春日君激昂吶喊的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤裸裸地表現出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿扭曲幻想的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君　你不是把臉埋在佐伯的雙峰之間了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每天在家貪婪地吸吮著運動服的香氣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用體操服在你邪惡的身體上四處摩擦麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就是這麼一個徹底的大變態麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就聽不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也是 今天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想些什麼 仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時教室的氣氛沒看到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑的傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連佐伯同學都用可疑的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有用運動服到處亂蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的繆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的維納斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就扔進焚燒爐燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要　停手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就覺得身體裡充斥著躁動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至想將身體深處的慾望大聲吶喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種躁動難以忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至覺得整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在我難耐的躁動中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死的話比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定也是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我簽訂契約的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後 每天放學以後都和我一起過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯同學的體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊緊地貼著我的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄然地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發出罪惡之香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近根本沒一起玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了 那樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後一個禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後每天都一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那麼正大光明的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一被學校那幫傢伙發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道被說成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說「怎樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快一點 春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春日君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我的手的味道很好聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聞聞看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流經小鎮的最大的河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那條河的草叢中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽著仲村那些虛幻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 天已經很暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天差不多就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸媽不會生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都這麼晚回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日用這手在佐伯的體操服上來回撫摸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身上四處摩擦來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說我沒有做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你喜歡佐伯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡她哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候穿著佐伯的體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫不了作文的話口述吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我想今天真的先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天也變暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都跑去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和山田玩稍微玩了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 有這麼玩的必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你爸爸都沒吃飯在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高男已經是中學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩玩不是也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽也是擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次至少打個電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 快吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還殘留著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村到底想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對仲村來說我算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個世界都在我難耐的躁動中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死的話比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村大概
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用和我一樣的想法生存著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定也是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對佐伯的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有對她的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是如此的純粹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵啊 一大早的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在我哥哥房間裡發現了DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 懂得吧 DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣　來嘛春日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨礙我讀書了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了 怎麼辦亞衣醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天忘記交就塞到儲物櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上來了就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人昨天放學後偷的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次才剛剛發生佐伯的事情不久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村一直和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天放學做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由由的午餐費被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村 你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擋路了 滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說 說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天放學後打算回教室的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從以前開始就很奇怪啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一個人碎碎念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實不知道仲村在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這次的事和她沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證據都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 春日
