Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會選仲村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 你很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把客觀的考察情況後的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會那樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由 去和老師說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在冷靜下想想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客觀來看現在的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 已經發現了
